{
  "texts": [
    "Second, we included the user-perceived quality of the texts (labeled QualityScore).",
    "The measurement of this variable is described in Section 2.5.2.",
    "The saturated exploration model, which we will refer to as CALQ (Correctness-Author-Length-Quality), is specified in Eq. 3.",
    "Table 8 presents the variance and standard deviation of the random effects on the intercept for the CALQ model.",
    "Table 9 shows the estimates of the fixed effects and intercept for the CALQ model."
  ]
